    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在发行时获得豪华升级以领取独家奖励！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273480/extras/3c783cb507b613e944d78bc5db97d0b7.avif?t=1772104243\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273480/extras_big/3c783cb507b613e944d78bc5db97d0b7.webp?t=1772104243 width=1560 height=877 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>来自 nDreams Elevation——虚拟现实沉浸体验专家新创工作室的开创性电影式动作冒险之作。</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >化身一位身不由己的英雄，掌握非凡能力，踏入交错现实构成的危境世界。你的每一个动作都将左右命运。准备好跃入其中了吗？    </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>前所未有的沉浸体验</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全身感知与高度拟真的互动机制，让你在每一个瞬间都仿佛身临其境。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>身临其境的冒险旅程</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深入探索一个充满神话诅咒与待解之谜的壮丽世界。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>掌控每一场动作</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自由跳跃、攀爬、滑索穿越令人屏息的壮丽环境，在为 VR 精心打造的流畅、直观移动系统中尽情驰骋。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>流畅战斗体验</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与强大致命的敌人展开紧张刺激、瞬息万变的战斗交锋。 </p>",
